### OpenTelemetry Demo API Requests
### Update the port based on what's shown in Aspire Dashboard

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Basic Weather Forecast Endpoints

### Get Weather Forecast (default 5 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/WeatherForecast
Accept: application/json

### Get Weather Forecast with custom days
GET {{baseUrl}}/WeatherForecast?days=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Weather Forecast for specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/WeatherForecast/2025-08-10
Accept: application/json

### Test Error Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/WeatherForecast/error
Accept: application/json

### Test Slow Endpoint (default 2000ms)
GET {{baseUrl}}/WeatherForecast/slow
Accept: application/json

### Test Slow Endpoint with custom delay
GET {{baseUrl}}/WeatherForecast/slow?delayMs=5000
Accept: application/json

### Metrics Demo Endpoints

### Process Request with default complexity
GET {{baseUrl}}/Metrics/process
Accept: application/json

### Process Request with higher complexity
GET {{baseUrl}}/Metrics/process?complexity=3
Accept: application/json

### Batch Process (default 5 items)
GET {{baseUrl}}/Metrics/batch
Accept: application/json

### Batch Process with custom count
GET {{baseUrl}}/Metrics/batch?count=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/Metrics/status
Accept: application/json

### Advanced Telemetry Demos

### Baggage Propagation Demo
GET {{baseUrl}}/TelemetryDemo/baggage?userId=john123&tenantId=acme-corp
Accept: application/json

### Span Links Demo (Batch with linked spans)
GET {{baseUrl}}/TelemetryDemo/span-links?itemCount=10
Accept: application/json

