GET {{baseUrl}}/TelemetryDemo/metrics-demo
Accept: application/json

### Custom Telemetry Demo (Rich attributes and events)
GET {{baseUrl}}/TelemetryDemo/custom-telemetry?complexity=7
Accept: application/json

### Context Propagation Demo
GET {{baseUrl}}/TelemetryDemo/context-propagation
Accept: application/json

